item.title: sweet potato casserole
item.description: Ingredients 1 pound sweet potato boiled and mashed 1/2 cup sugar 1/4 teaspoon cinnamon 1/4 cup wheat flour 1/4 cup milk 2 tablespoons butter melted 2 beaten eggs 1/4 teaspoon salt Directions Mix the ingredients in the order they appear, beat to join them well. Pour into a greased mold and cook in a moderate heat oven for 20 to 30 minutes.
